# Next.js Patterns

## App Router

- Use App Router structure with `src/app/` directory
- Implement proper metadata in `layout.tsx`
- Use server components by default, client components when needed
- Leverage Next.js 15 features and optimizations

## Performance

- Use Turbopack for faster development builds
- Implement proper image optimization with Next.js Image component
- Use dynamic imports for code splitting
- Optimize bundle size with proper imports

## SEO and Metadata

- Define comprehensive metadata in [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
- Use proper favicon configuration
- Implement Open Graph and Twitter Card metadata
- Use semantic HTML structure

## Fonts

- Use Next.js font optimization with Google Fonts
- Implement IBM Plex Sans and IBM Plex Mono
- Use CSS custom properties for font variables
- Apply proper font loading strategies

## Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS with PostCSS configuration
- Implement proper CSS custom properties
- Use global styles in `globals.css`
- Apply consistent design tokens

## Development

- Use `npm run dev` with Turbopack for development
- Implement proper TypeScript configuration
- Use ESLint for code quality
- Follow Next.js best practices for file organization